Class AlertRandom

  • java.lang.Object
    • htds.AlertRandom

  • public class AlertRandom
extends java.lang.Object
    This class generates random data structures for testing purposes The following structures are supported: 1- Random ID number 2- Random Phone number 3- Random Color 4- Random Date 5- Random String 6- Random String Array 7- Random Alert 8- Random AlertLog
    Author:
    Qutaiba
